</p></context><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_64BB077525D643BAA0D00A934918884D" class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Clip. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Maintenance tray and lid. 
</p></li><li id="LI_929C0F12811B4096BB70DA320BD9C6C8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves: 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-E0744C42-ABAC-49E6-AC01-06127BEDE6A3" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-BD2EB3CE-E413-4C39-80F5-CD2457F8C3EA" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1BE61C74-E5E1-4927-9260-FB5959D1D8CE-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1BE61C74-E5E1-4927-9260-FB5959D1D8CE-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to refill</title><table id="GUID-BDB87D50-9E70-4086-AC9E-FA7970C76B0D" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Go to Cold SDS. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the top cover. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the light shield (for stray light prevention). 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See 
<xref keyref="05DISA54" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-A74FC275-9488-4456-BC7A-5547780981BC.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 05 How to remove the light shield (for stray light prevention)?>05 How to remove the light shield (for stray light prevention)</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Slide the printhead carriage to the middle of the platen (print surface). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place a sheet of media on the platen. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place a maintenance tray on the sheet. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Close the 2 valves of the printhead. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Disconnect the ink tube from printhead. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Guide the ink tube in the maintenance tray. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Lock the tube to the maintenance tray with a clip. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the valve of the tube. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-D58A7270-8D65-4381-912F-8445269E0D6D" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1BE61C74-E5E1-4927-9260-FB5959D1D8CE-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1BE61C74-E5E1-4927-9260-FB5959D1D8CE-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">10 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Do SDS test 
<xref keyref="SDS02-6-001" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-AB12A141-328E-4CED-9904-40E53DC5D78D.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02-6-001 Fill ink tube(s) [Special Tests]?>02-6-001 Fill ink tube(s) [Special Tests]</xref>. 
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Select the correct channel and 400 seconds (Time to flush the complete volume of the ink tube). 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">When there is still air left in the ink tube, you can extend the 400 seconds by pressing continue in the SDS test. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Result : tube is air free if the ink flow has a heartbeat rhythm from the pump. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">11 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Close the 2 valves of printhead. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">12 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Connect the ink tube to the printhead. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">13 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the 2 valves of printhead. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">14 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the maintenance tray from the sheet. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">15 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the sheet from the platen. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">16 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the light shield (for stray light prevention). 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See 
<xref keyref="05DISA54" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-A74FC275-9488-4456-BC7A-5547780981BC.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 05 How to remove the light shield (for stray light prevention)?>05 How to remove the light shield (for stray light prevention)</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">17 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Go to warm SDS. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">18 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Do SDS test 
<xref keyref="SDS21-6-005" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-EC09B37A-4C4A-4AF7-8C63-0FBD950660CC.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 21-6-005 Service prints [Special Tests]?>21-6-005 Service prints [Special Tests]</xref>. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Select PQT Matte Speciality (8 pass) on the right roll.
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">19 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Dispose of the maintenance tray, gloves etcetera according to the local procedures. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table><note id="GUID-312D4B65-7282-4283-8CAB-B2C44A6ED5FB" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">If you are confused about the indicated ink levels please see the explanation in this document : 
<xref keyref="02FUNC02" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-B182E6B2-C192-49EF-A460-6AE139F1F6CD.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="concept"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02 The function of the ink level sensors?>02 The function of the ink level sensors</xref> 
</p></note></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-5FD80AE8-25CD-48D0-A58E-331C6E9FF682.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Adjustment</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
